parkingLots.name: Jim's House
parkingLots.description: Jim offers up to 10 spaces in both his front and back yard. Short easy walk to and from the staduim

parkingLots.name: Craighead and Bransford
parkingLots.description: Just across the streed from Fair Park. Easy access to tailgaiting at Fair Park, but difficult to leave due to proximity to staduim and pedestrian traffic.

parkingLots.name: Fort Negley
parkingLots.description: Free parking provided by NSC. Good 25 minute walk to stadium, or you can ride the shuttle for $20 roundtrip

parkingLots.name: NSC provided Lot 5
parkingLots.description: Season Passes for these lots are sold out. A limited number of passes are made available each week

parkingLots.name: Smokin Thighs
parkingLots.description: Great spot if you want to grab some wings and loaded potato salad before the match

parkingLots.name: Stacys Favorite Lot
parkingLots.description: just a few spots. Get here early!

parkingLots.name: My 2nd favorite spot
parkingLots.description: consider yourself lucky if you get a spot here

parkingLots.name: ACT Security
parkingLots.description: consider yourself lucky if you get a spot here

supporterGroups.name: The Roadies
supporterGroups.description: The Roadies have fun, maybe have a pop, and lose our voices singing and cheering for Nashville Soccer Club, but being a Supporters Group means more to us. In addition to being a group that welcomes all who cheer for NSC, we actively give back to the community.

supporterGroups.name: The Assembly
supporterGroups.description: Welcome to the “Circus”, an Assembly of fans near and far, where new and old fans of the beautiful game can come as you are.

supporterGroups.name: Eastern Front
supporterGroups.description: Founded by Middle Tennessee footballers in 2017, Eastern Front is a Recognized Supporters Group designed to enhance the Nashville SC experience, provide a match-focused social setting, and promote the Beautiful Game.

supporterGroups.name: Music City Heaters
supporterGroups.description: So, if you’re interested in joining an awesome fellowship of guys and gals that loves NSC, but doesn’t take itself too seriously, come introduce yourself and we’ll get to know each other over a tall, crisp, refreshing Black Cherry White Claw.

supporterGroups.name: La Brigada de Oro
supporterGroups.description: Founded by our belief “UNITED WE ARE STRONGER” We welcome and embrace diversity and all cultural backgrounds. This is the basis for our club as we are La Brigada De Oro. A brigade of fans. “EN LA UNION ESTA LA FUERZA”.

supporterGroups.name: The MixTape 615
supporterGroups.description: Welcome to the Mixtape, Inc. My Verse. Our Song. Nashville’s Soundtrack.
